# Equality of two records (positional).
*eq2(a as Vec of i64, b as Vec of i64) returns bool
    a.get(0) equals b.get(0) and a.get(1) equals b.get(1)

*main
    a is vec()
    a.push(3)
    a.push(4)
    b is vec()
    b.push(3)
    b.push(4)
    c is vec()
    c.push(3)
    c.push(5)
    log eq2(a, b)
    log eq2(a, c)
